posts.post_title: WTB WTTF: T206 PSA 4 Non Standard Backs
posts.post_content:
Looking for PSA 4 non-standard backs (Sweet Cap, Piedmont) in PSA 4 in any HOFer, Cicotte, Burns, and Chase.  Trying to add a few back variations to my collection.  The only thing that I really look for is that the image and back advertisement not be sloped in any way.  Figured this time I'd also put some trade bait out there.  All PSA 4:

Brown Chicago Shirt SC
Chance Yellow Portrait PM
Ed Collins Portrait SOV
Matty Portrait PM
McGraw Glove at Hip SC (with wet sheet transfer)

Hopefully a possible trade raises some interest.
